  ('optician-moex-02339', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', 'cm的距離受測者報告呈現複視（diplopia），視標再慢慢往後移，在離受測者前方20 cm的距離報告 呈現回復成單一視標，此時受測者可能是下列何種情況？', '["受測者有弱視", "受測者調節不足（accommodation insufficiency）", "受測者內聚不足（convergence insufficiency）", "受測者有抑制現象"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02340', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關虛性相對調節力（NRA）及實性相對調節力（PRA）的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["此檢測不能使用綜合驗光儀測量", "測量虛性相對調節力時要加負度數（minus）鏡片", "虛性與實性相對調節力測量在雙眼狀態下（binocular condition）進行", "在測量時必須使用患者的遠用瞳距（distance PD）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02341', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '不用綜合驗光儀，只用視網膜檢影鏡，你在工作距離67 cm處取得患者遠點（共軛點）時，則此患者有 下列何種屈光不正？', '["-2.00 D近視", "+2.00 D遠視", "+1.50 D遠視", "-1.50 D近視"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02342', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一項檢測，可以得到角膜表面最完整的弧度資料？', '["角膜弧度儀（keratometer）", "自動驗光儀（autorefractor）", "普拉西多圓錐盤（Placido disc）", "角膜地圖儀（corneal topography）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02343', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '角膜弧度儀測出42.50 D在180度軸，45.00 D在90度軸時，所顯示的角膜散光度數是下列何者？', '["-2.50DC×090", "-2.50DC×180", "-1.75DC×090", "-1.75DC×180"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02344', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '圓錐角膜及非對稱性散光，皆可透過波前技術偵測到高階像差，最常見的高階像差為下列何者？', '["球面像差（spherical aberration）", "彗星像差（coma aberration）", "三葉草像差（trefoil aberration）", "屈光異常（refractive errors）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02345', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '受檢者為46歲，有-1.00DS 的近視，近一年來覺得查看地圖上的小文字時越來越困難。經過測量後發現 不戴任何矯正眼鏡時可以看清楚的最近距離為25 cm，此受檢者還有多少的調節幅度？', '["1.00 D", "3.00 D", "4.00 D", "5.00 D"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02346', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若角膜散光軸位於120～150度之間，此為何種類型的散光？', '["斜散光（oblique astigmatism）", "水晶體散光（lenticular astigmatism）", "順散光（with-the-rule astigmatism）", "逆散光（against-the-rule astigmatism）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02347', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '進行視網膜鏡檢查時，下列何項作法無助於控制受測者的調節力？', '["檢查者的頭擋住受測眼的視線", "視標距離儘量放遠", "儘量用大的視標", "視標可加上紅/綠濾鏡"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bc120393b81a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1e37b2c594ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
